ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd2324f55a476cce1f1c9586855663539726906","tid":38431,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係習派出手<br />\n所有江派同西環支持既都應該選唔到<br />\n葉劉同林鄭都輸<br />\n如果今次唔係品客<br />\n即事真果個未出</blockquote><br />\n胡官？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9500d0d44c2b39503b262561be66fc22e50c1e87","tid":38431,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國內戰 + 中美大戰 同時爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbattlefield 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e91f538c78d85d1e9b6dfc058ef5693d47d15e","tid":38431,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"繼續吹<br />\n上個月秘魯見面唔撚直接講，要派人黎講? 咁撚on9? 名又無講乜撚都得，咁你個獨家話上個月見完面雜總hehe 689 要佢入後宮都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2b1d49387a11cb7edf355116adaeeeefba5289","tid":38431,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>傳乜鳩令<br />\n2016年仲要搵人傳令<br />\n打個電話比689 叫佢唔撚洗做已經得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔打電話咪用佢地大陸微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n決定下任特首，咁大件事打個電話就算？<br />\n<br />\n以後d領導人唔洗外訪啦， 去日本就line 安培,  去美帝就whatsapp侵侵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加上中紀委巡視組早前點出港澳辦「六宗罪」，據悉，中聯辦、<strong>港澳辦如中聯辦主任張曉明之流有意阻擋，令習近平政令不能傳達到香港。</strong>故習只能靠特使傳達命令。<br />\n<br />\n外交點同內政比<br />\n其實如果雜總d所謂指令傳唔到落黎就代表中共根本無能力管咁大片土地</blockquote><br />\n呢個都唔係第一日既事黎既啦<br />\n如果唔係咁,支那既地方債都唔會搞到依家咁"},{"pid":"077ecc348ed78633bcb9e8cdcb45a4d30e49afa9","tid":38431,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支共狗至叻神又佢鬼又係佢！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我9錢一早講左：等睇N隊管治狗隊恆常化....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n枱面：搵班叫做似D人既港英餘孽外藉僱傭狗，尤其扮鬼鬍鬚繼續打門面工幫手賣港賣雞棚洗衣機！！<br />\n枱底：繼續養住一大班乜撚研鳩會乜撚人大乜撚主席適時放狗咬人做衰野：689，鳩董，左耳陳，西環，護法etc</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"db2d62eae5786ccb083a21227ef991c63b0d953e","tid":38431,"uid":29799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"又無度作故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfc2fcee8767196f92bc522f388deea7009d59d","tid":38431,"uid":29799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又無度作故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d667903e2712cc007d81ec916fa509c4ec20d1ed","tid":38431,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"大紀完"},{"pid":"51054b5fe43c627dc570c5a48ec6fc6a6291465e","tid":38431,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T22:00:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>流到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/111310_a0701099f5c8598d26d24311a845f5ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F111310_a0701099f5c8598d26d24311a845f5ae.jpg&h=25ce2566&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/